# Later rules win: the generic text rule comes first, then the fixture
# override — fixture bytes (BOM/CRLF) must be stored exactly as authored.
# eol=lf forces LF on checkout regardless of the runner's core.autocrlf,
# so Prettier's endOfLine: "lf" holds on Windows CI as well as locally.
* text=auto eol=lf
fixtures/** -text
docs/screenshot.png binary
apps/desktop/src-tauri/icons/** binary
